{"tid":839583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[瑞典又中]中國男子在非洲迦納花園隨地便溺","createTime":"2018-09-28T04:58:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T05:52:11.000Z","uid":75969,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"37a874dfda273b287a0d17de7719ba7b332ddb97","tid":839583,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T04:58:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpM0wzsA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpM0wzsA.jpg&h=4bf722de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">最近一名中國人在西非國家迦納的一處花園裡大便，當地民眾發現後，要求他用鏟子將他的糞便收拾乾淨。（圖擷取自Instagram）<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕最近一名中國人在西非國家迦納的一處花園裡大便，當地民眾發現後，要求他用鏟子將他的糞便收拾乾淨。當地人問這名中國人，是不是也會在自己的國家隨地便溺，這名中國人只是不斷道歉，不願正面回應。外國媒體批評，中國人無法無天，公開無視迦納的法律。<br />\n<br />\n奈及利亞《pulse》報導，一名網友最近在社群網路Instagram上分享一段影片，指一名住在迦納的中國大叔，跑到一處花園裡大便，被當地民眾抓到，要求他用鏟子將他糞便清乾淨。中國男子被問到是不是也會在自己的國家隨地便溺，他則不願回應，只是不斷道歉。<br />\n<br />\n報導提到，這段影片雖然有點搞笑，但仍存在需要解決的嚴重問題，在過去幾年內，迦納湧入大量的中國人，他們在當地無法無天，公開無視迦納的法律。<br />\n<br />\n外國網友表示，「可憐的傢伙」、「你知道廁所在哪裡嗎？」、「中國人好像都這樣」、「逮捕他！」、「這非常糟糕」、「不應該用鏟子，應該用雙手清他的糞便」、「自找麻煩的傢伙」、「替他感到難過」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2564145\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2564145&d=35VR44aBLSg6O01mXEyuI54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=f4052bca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2564145&h=fb3bdfed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2564145</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n片:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/BoOL0L2hFkx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBoOL0L2hFkx&d=35VR44aBLSg6O01mXEyuI54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=ead02ae1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBoOL0L2hFkx&h=642dd27d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/BoOL0L2hFkx</a>"},{"pid":"f79d82e7d463b7e321b63b2d3a72aa7536a9488b","tid":839583,"uid":26429,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T05:03:51.000Z","msg":"啲外國人都打橫黎講既，唔隨地大小便點叫中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81fbfbd07e736a345a77ae9d3f3af10e640d26e0","tid":839583,"uid":90735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T05:05:05.000Z","msg":"中国人係咪唔識屙完屎先出街？"},{"pid":"1091d32ee06c40ba492f631df089b7fd31f5cc24","tid":839583,"uid":43009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T05:06:32.000Z","msg":"中國男子被問到是不是也會在自己的國家隨地便溺，他則不願回應<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91a0fa02bdc934bf05c07661a0a4c1b86dbdbe73","tid":839583,"uid":75072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T05:06:40.000Z","msg":"唔俾人屙屎簡直係挑戰人類道德底線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f94d153db5c571f0c57bc5229b72ee29aecc1a8","tid":839583,"uid":22422,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T05:06:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/28/130652_3ca7a87194a5735396d08ecc89b12b98.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F28%2F130652_3ca7a87194a5735396d08ecc89b12b98.png&h=1754e1ca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1330832c99bcb985b5ec8b12e0b10f70fa21fbc","tid":839583,"uid":98289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f94d153db5c571f0c57bc5229b72ee29aecc1a8","tid":839583,"uid":22422,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T05:06:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2